import React, {useState} from "react"
import './App.css';
import AllRecipes from "./Components/AllRecipes";
import HighMarginRecipes from "./Components/HighMarginRecipes";
import IsDisabled from "./Components/IsDisabled";
import IsIncorrect from "./Components/IsIncorrect";
import IsUntagged from "./Components/IsUntagged";
import LowMarginRecipes from "./Components/LowMarginRecipes";
import TopFluctuatingRecipes from "./Components/TopFluctuatingRecipes";
import {Tabs, Tab, Card,Container,Row,Col } from "react-bootstrap"
import 'bootstrap/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css'
import demo from "./Components/demo";


function App() {

    const [key, setKey] = useState('incorrect');

    return (
        <>
            <Container className="mt-3" style={{maxWidth:"100%"}}>
                <Row>
                    <Col md>
                        <Card className="border rounded text-center">
                            <Card.Header style={{backgroundColor:"#f5f3f9"}}>High Margin Recipes</Card.Header>
                            <Card.Body>
                                <HighMarginRecipes />
                            </Card.Body>
                        </Card>
                    </Col>
                    <Col md>
                        <Card className="text-center border rounded">
                            <Card.Header>Low Margin Recipes</Card.Header>
                            <Card.Body>
                                <LowMarginRecipes />
                            </Card.Body>
                        </Card>
                    </Col>
                    <Col md>
                        <Card className="text-center border rounded">
                            <Card.Header>Top Fluctuating Recipes</Card.Header>
                            <Card.Body>
                                <TopFluctuatingRecipes />
                            </Card.Body>
                        </Card>
                    </Col>
                </Row>
                
            </Container>
            
            
            <Tabs className="myTabs m-3 " id="controlled-tab-example" activeKey={key} onSelect={(k) => setKey(k)}>
                <Tab className="m-3" eventKey="allrecipes" title="ALL RECIPE(S)">
                    <AllRecipes />
                </Tab>
                <Tab className="m-3" eventKey="incorrect" title="INCORRECT">
                    <IsIncorrect />  
                </Tab>
                <Tab className="m-3" eventKey="untagged" title="UNTAGGED">
                    <IsUntagged />
                </Tab>
                <Tab className="m-3" eventKey="disabled" title="DISABLED">
                    <IsDisabled />
                </Tab>
            </Tabs>
        </>
    );
}

export default App;
